    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>OP said they didn't want a for loop but in case anyone does:</p>\n<pre><code>int[] subArr = new int[end - start];\n\nfor (int i = 0; i &lt; end - start; i++){\n    subArr[i] = sourceArr[i + start];\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
